# For more info on HTTP files go to https://aka.ms/vs/httpfile
@host = https://localhost:7095

### Log in as the admin (Admin role, STANDARD tier, joined 2024-01-15)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@codewithmukesh.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Log in as the manager (Manager role, PREMIUM tier, joined 2026-04-20)
# @name managerLogin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@codewithmukesh.com",
  "password": "Manager123!"
}

### Log in as the regular user (User role, FREE tier, joined 2024-08-01)
# @name userLogin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@codewithmukesh.com",
  "password": "User123!"
}

### Pro insights as admin - 200 via the AdminOverrideHandler (role, not subscription)
GET {{host}}/api/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Pro insights as manager - 200 via the PremiumSubscriptionHandler (subscription, not role)
GET {{host}}/api/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{managerLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Pro insights as regular user - 403 (no handler succeeds: free tier, no Admin role)
GET {{host}}/api/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Publish a document - 200 between 09:00-18:00 UTC, 403 outside
POST {{host}}/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Veterans lounge - [MinimumTenure(6)] via IAuthorizationRequirementData (user: 200, joined 2024)
GET {{host}}/api/veterans-lounge
Authorization: Bearer {{userLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Veterans lounge as manager - 403 (joined 2026-04-20, under 6 months)
GET {{host}}/api/veterans-lounge
Authorization: Bearer {{managerLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Imperative check - DELETE explains the failure instead of a bare 403
DELETE {{host}}/api/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.$.token}}

### Fallback policy in action - unknown-to-auth endpoint without a token = 401
GET {{host}}/api/insightsB